{"tid":1585794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以武抗黑, 絕非獅鳥!","createTime":"2019-09-21T17:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T18:09:27.000Z","uid":34144,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b42ea8989cacdb05e6b7509dc24dba96de2af66","tid":1585794,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:21:39.000Z","msg":"好多手足會用私了/獅鳥嚟形容前線手足英勇抗黑嘅義舉,一嚟未能彰顯手足嘅正當性,二嚟外媒照報嗰陣實在唔好睇。<br />\n<br />\n名不正則言不順。手足做嘅係以武抗黑,以武制暴。係大義所在,絕非一己私怨。<br />\n<br />\n另附元朗事件真相:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=394841064741560&amp;id=178965725523592&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D394841064741560%26id%3D178965725523592%26_rdr&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=433a1ca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=394841064741560&amp;id=178965725523592&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n感謝一眾勇武義士無私付出,感謝 First Aid 手足堅守崗位,每一次出嚟夢遊,因為有你哋,每次有手足受傷之後都好快得到幫助, 洗傷口,包紮,甚至係CPR.仲好記得831,喺太子站外求班黑警畀佢入去救人嗰位FA, 多謝你哋一直嘅堅持同付出。<br />\n<br />\n出過嚟夢遊嘅手足,請諗一諗每次有人受傷,暈低時,全場大叫first aid 嘅情境。FA手足咁耐嘅貢獻,救返幾多參與呢場革命嘅手足,相信大家都有目共睹。<br />\n<br />\n大家都係手足, 如果有不滿, 大可以提醒對方點去改善,一齊努力,下次改進! <br />\n<br />\n不指責,不割席,不分化,不篤灰。"},{"pid":"4f45e40210ef261923e6fa1adbbb5d2e29336dcd","tid":1585794,"uid":262096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b2262109eb888bb434526190b2d14f108ab779","tid":1585794,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:26:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9169e5361656f66b5b398c8af42b7d7575fd879","tid":1585794,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:27:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f510a80d5b0b2052af3c2a1b84c5befdcb04489","tid":1585794,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco